	   <tr><td colspan=2>Try unequipping your secondary weapon; your secondary won't get any double attacks until the end of level 29, and it'll just distract you if you're looking for a double attack. You'll recognize double attack if you see two attack messages coming up at the exact same time. Also, you probably won't see it working much with only 18 skill in it. Have you ever seen the message &quot;You have increased your skill in double attack (#)&quot;? If you don't see that by the time you level to 17, you may want to find some DEX equipment. Not only does DEX help you improve it faster, but you will see it succeeding more as well.<br>&nbsp;<br>Daviv McD (Retired)<br>32nd Dwarf Rogue<br>Lords of Belterra<br>Xegony</td></tr>
