t lightly armored mages, do more damage over time. <br>- using a tombcarver 5 dam 17 del still they get away because of lag in game or i somehow lose around corner for sec <br>10) use more mana drain poisons <br>- same as 2<br>11) get some form of device that allows you to cancell magic. Damage shields are a real nuisance. High resists help soften them but only a cancel magic really does the job. <br>- pumice stones i hear are 20pp yes ill have to do this but i sure hope there an instant cancel if there more than 3 secs im dead again because it only takes 2 to 3 hits anyway and if i get lucky and its 3 i barely have hps to move.<br>12) use even more mana drain poisons. - same as 2<br><br><br>A rogue is most effective when he/she can choose the time and conditions for the fight. Think like an assassin and not a street brawler. Don't duel someone unless you have prepared to duel that person well in advance and have the proper tools on your person. On PVP servers this can't always be helped. In that case get MR up to avoid roots and run away. You can come back and nail the jerk later when he/she is medding and not being well guarded. Never fight unless the odds are heavily tipped in your favor. Is that fair? No, but you are a rogue. What do you care about fair?<br><br>- I dont initiate the fights against casters they initiate against me because i feel they know they are going to win 90% of all fights against melee peeps.  <br><br>So for now here are my plans:<br><br>1.  Hang around with more friends to be stronger in numbers.  <br>2.  Run around naked and dont use good equipment &amp; mr stuff when traveling, when possible pk casters are around, or you are lower than 50% in health.  That away if I am killed I can save mr gear and keep acumulating instead of buying over and over.  <br>3.  Lvl as fast as possible to 18 because I cannot apply poison tell then.  And save as much poison for this time comes.<br>4.  By pumice stones at the 20pp when possible.<br>5.  Get buffed by higher lvls as much as possible.  Hate begging but o well must survive.<br>6.  SCREAM BLOOD MURDER in shout message when caster hitting you around corner and u cant hit back with arrows because it says you cant see target.  <br><br>I have analized and anaziled, questioned and questioned and gotten good responses from you all, appreciate your HELP!!!!<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
